  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/4d1fd7d518ea23bbdf236662e2969bff.avif?t=1769957979\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras_big/4d1fd7d518ea23bbdf236662e2969bff.webp?t=1769957979 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A nightmare you can't wake up from, a pain that won't heal...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this unique survival horror game, classical music intertwines with psychological terror to create an suffocatingly eerie atmosphere. You will play as Alice, an ordinary girl who wakes up to find herself trapped in a constantly shifting, bizarre world. An orphanage shrouded in ice, monsters lurking in the shadows, and intricate puzzles—every step is filled with danger and the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive, you must gather supplies, evade pursuit, and unravel the secrets hidden in the darkness. But as the truth gradually comes to light, will you be able to bear the cruel reality behind it all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Features of This Game:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.poster.avif?t=1769957979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.webm?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.mp4?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action Shooting:</strong><br>Use a variety of firearms to defeat enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Map Exploration:</strong><br>Step by step, explore the eerie and terrifying orphanage. Collect different items to unlock new areas, while being prepared for sudden, inexplicable changes that may occur during your exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management:</strong><br>Gather and wisely utilize limited resources to survive by any means necessary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle Solving:</strong><br>Collect information, solve various puzzles, and uncover the final truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.poster.avif?t=1769957979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.webm?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.mp4?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/4d1fd7d518ea23bbdf236662e2969bff.avif?t=1769957979\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras_big/4d1fd7d518ea23bbdf236662e2969bff.webp?t=1769957979 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A nightmare you can't wake up from, a pain that won't heal...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this unique survival horror game, classical music intertwines with psychological terror to create an suffocatingly eerie atmosphere. You will play as Alice, an ordinary girl who wakes up to find herself trapped in a constantly shifting, bizarre world. An orphanage shrouded in ice, monsters lurking in the shadows, and intricate puzzles—every step is filled with danger and the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To survive, you must gather supplies, evade pursuit, and unravel the secrets hidden in the darkness. But as the truth gradually comes to light, will you be able to bear the cruel reality behind it all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Features of This Game:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.poster.avif?t=1769957979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.webm?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/b628f08c27fb52dbc0425783304ebc4f.mp4?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action Shooting:</strong><br>Use a variety of firearms to defeat enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Map Exploration:</strong><br>Step by step, explore the eerie and terrifying orphanage. Collect different items to unlock new areas, while being prepared for sudden, inexplicable changes that may occur during your exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource Management:</strong><br>Gather and wisely utilize limited resources to survive by any means necessary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzle Solving:</strong><br>Collect information, solve various puzzles, and uncover the final truth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.poster.avif?t=1769957979\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.webm?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3193730/extras/5a5d4403eac28db82baf24563011b649.mp4?t=1769957979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
